com.emc.ecs.nfsclient.nfs

Class NfsPreOpAttributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.ecs.nfsclient.nfs.NfsPreOpAttributes

  • public class NfsPreOpAttributes
extends java.lang.Object
    These pre-operation attributes are part of weak cache consistency data, as specified by RFC 1813 (https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1813).
